    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>cashew nuts</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden, then transfer to a  bowl and set aside, reserve the pan</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
