    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>butternut squash cubes</strong> and <strong>onion wedges</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to caramelise</p>",
