    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[400ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [500ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
