    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once starting to caramelise, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>ginger paste </strong>and <strong>red Thai curry paste </strong>to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant add the <strong>vegetable stock </strong>and cook, covered, for 7-8 min or until starting to soften</p>",
