    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once starting to soften, add your <strong>halved green beans</strong>, <strong>toasted cashew nuts </strong>and <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>and mix to combine</p><p>Cook, covered, for a further 8-9 min or until the butternut squash cubes and green beans are tender – this is your <strong>butternut squash & cashew coconut curry</strong></p>",
